<div class="comment-content">
<p>I am actually unsure if the chuunibyou is strong with these people, or not. Their existence and way of talking is inflated if you can only imagine that they just poofed into existence with such an absurd background, but their absurdity lessens when you try to imagine them as real people, who just lived very abnormal lives.</p>
<p>Xuan&#8217;s etiquette is a bit irking, though.</p>
</div> 
